{
  "id": "adv_event_2510_01_03",
  "title": "私達の青春謳歌 3話 出し物考案中",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日、星見プロ東京寮にて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うーん、オリジナルの劇……プカミちゃん……",
      "startTime": 2.5000000756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁぁ、あかん！　すぐ『ぷりエン』に引っ張られる",
      "startTime": 9.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4600
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あれ、優ちゃんまた脚本書いてるんだ。『劇団★見』",
      "startTime": 14.3333334089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "の次回作？　不思議の国のアリス大好評だったもんね！",
      "startTime": 19.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回は再来週学園祭で生徒会がするミュージカルの",
      "startTime": 24.3333334089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "脚本なんよ。せやけどなーんかうまいこといかんくてな",
      "startTime": 28.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだったんだ",
      "startTime": 34.3333298485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "準備、大変だよね……何に悩んでたの？",
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この間うちらがやった『ぷりてぃーエンジェル』の舞台",
      "startTime": 41.13333112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "を学園祭で見たいって声が生徒達から沢山あがってて",
      "startTime": 44.4666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さすがに権利の問題でそれは出来んから",
      "startTime": 50.3666644533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "オリジナルのストーリーを考えてるんやけど難しくてな",
      "startTime": 53.7329484467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『ぷりエン』ぽいけど『ぷりエン』ではないオリジ",
      "startTime": 58.8999977867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ナリティのある戦う女の子の話を描きたいんやけど……",
      "startTime": 61.9666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バトルものだよね……うーん……あ、最近千紗ちゃんに",
      "startTime": 67.0666644533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "オススメしてもらった映画はバトルものだったよ！",
      "startTime": 73.7000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "参考になるか分かんないけど、神様に仕える聖なる",
      "startTime": 77.4666664879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "シスターさん達が悪魔を祓って人々を救うお話で……",
      "startTime": 81.6889703857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "シスター！？　めっちゃええな！",
      "startTime": 86.2000059248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "戦うシスターなんて舞台上での衣装映えもええやろし！",
      "startTime": 89.333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それに絶対、瑠依ちゃんに似合うやん……！",
      "startTime": 93.9333438357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "もう絶対可愛い……ああ、うちを祓ってほしい……",
      "startTime": 98.1000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かるよ！　もし琴乃ちゃんがシスターになったら",
      "startTime": 104.6666771691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "私も祓われたいって思うもん！　うへへ……",
      "startTime": 107.9666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "よし、うちと瑠依ちゃんが戦うシスターになる物語で",
      "startTime": 112.4666771691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "決まりや！　ほんまおおきにな、渚ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 116.7333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 122.0833438357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はあ……それでシスターの話になったのね",
      "startTime": 123.1333438357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "一言ぐらい相談してくれても良かったのに",
      "startTime": 128.1000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 131.6887408694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はっ！　ごめんな、締め切りが近くて焦ってもうた……",
      "startTime": 131.6887408694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "い、勢いで衣装の発注まで昨晩済ませてもうてて……",
      "startTime": 137.3000012715,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13433.333333399985
